	//			* dates only
	//			|	* yyyy
	//			|	* yyyy-MM
	//			|	* yyyy-MM-dd
	// 			* times only, with an optional time zone appended
	//			|	* THH:mm
	//			|	* THH:mm:ss
	//			|	* THH:mm:ss.SSS
	// 			* and "datetimes" which could be any combination of the above
